title: Hampton v Wozniacki - Eastbourne 2013 SF
description:
Eastbourne 2013, Semi-Final, Hampton v Wozniacki, capture of SD broadcast.

Transcoded from 576i/25fps MPEG-TS, ~3400 Kbps to 576p x264 using ffmpeg with settings -c:v libx264 -crf 21 -preset veryfast -tune animation -vf "yadif=0:-1:0" -c:a libfdk_aac -b:a 128000.


In two files: intro (short interview with Jamie Hampton) and match (uncut as broadcast, no adverts).
